You can create code constructs using statement completion.
Start typing a method declaration, a method call or a statement such as
if, do -while, try -catch, or return.
Press Ctrl+Shift+Enter to complete the statement into a syntactically correct construct.

使用语句补全地功能，你能够创建代码结构。
开始键入方法声明、方法调用或者一个语句。
比如 if, do-while, try-catch, 或者return。

按下 Ctrl + Shift + Enter 来 把语句补全到 语法正确的结构中